XRootD Lustre Quota Plugin
=======================================

This Repository contains the code to alter a dataservers behaviour so that xrdfs spaceinfo
returns the executings user's group's lustre quota statistics instead.
Setup
======

This plugin is loaded by the XRootD Server. In order to accomplish this, it is
necessary to indicate the server where the plugin is by adding the following
line to the server's configuration file:

  ofs.osslib /path/to/libLustreOss.so

This project uses the lustre c - api found in (lustre/utils) 
(( HINT: compile with ./configure '--disable-server' '--disable-modules' '--prefix=/to/where/ever')) 
